      "message": "Confirmed. These PDB fans are only detected via GPIODeviceDetect.\n\nThere is no EEPROM-based FRU device or other inventory source\n(frudevice/entity-manager/etc.) for these PDB fan entries.\n\nExample inventory entry after fan insertion:\n```\nroot@bmc:~# mfg-tool inventory 2\u003e/dev/null | jq \u0027with_entries(select(.key | test(\"PDB2_FAN\")))\u0027\n{\n  \"system/board/PDB2_FAN4\": {\n    \"Decorator.Asset\": {\n      \"Manufacturer\": \"Unknown\",\n      \"Model\": \"Unknown\",\n      \"PartNumber\": \"Unknown\",\n      \"SerialNumber\": \"Unknown\",\n      \"SparePartNumber\": \"05-100368\"\n    },\n    \"Item.Board\": {\n      \"Name\": \"PDB2_FAN4\",\n      \"Type\": \"Board\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```",
